        <span begin="1.112" end="1.396">of</span>
        <span begin="1.396" end="1.458">the</span>
        <span begin="1.458" end="1.720">song.</span>
        <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是歌曲的第一行。</span>
      </p>
