        <span begin="3.680" end="4.280">words.</span>
        <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">第二行来了更多词。</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="4.280" end="6.160" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1">
        <span begin="4.280" end="4.425">A</span>
