        <span begin="5.878" end="6.160">verse.</span>
        <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">第三行完成这节。</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="6.160" end="7.820" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1">
        <span begin="6.160" end="6.350">The</span>
