        <span begin="9.200" end="9.540">la</span>
        <span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">唱着啦啦啦啦</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="9.540" end="12.360" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1">
        <span begin="9.540" end="9.790">This</span>
